data.description: Direct Gulf Access, Luxury, TURNKEY, Home has NEVER been flooded!  Completely gutted & remodeled in fall of 2021. This is a home features: FULL home propane generator, New Roof (2019), New A/C 2019,  RV Pad with 50 AMP service installed, plumbing available for additional 1/2 bath (bathroom was turned into a gun closet), New Septic system and Hurricane Shutters on all Windows. It is GORGEOUS inside and boasts an extra large outdoor paved area. You MUST see this beauty!  SELLERS ARE MOTIVATED bring your offers!  Located in Charlotte Shores Community with *optional* (very low) HOA's that gain access to Marina, Boat slips, Launch Pads, and Boat Park. Less than 15 min to Open water and 30min to Cayo Costa, Cabbage Key- Boaters Paradise!   DOES NOT CONVEY: Bar Stools, Antique Chest in office, desk, lamp and desk chair, white book shelf, Bed in First Bedroom, nightstand, lamp, Stained glass artwork in 1st bedroom,  Master Bedroom Tall Dresser, night stand, lamp, TV,  All Artwork, Dishes and all items in shed, All sound bars, Chairs on patio,
